data.text:
CONTACT

MAY 2015:

[C.E. Chambers is Diana Einarsen's pseudonym: please read the "About" section. She worked for a newspaper as an interviewer and as a film critic and has also worked as a paid freelance journalist. She also donates her work on occasion.]

Welcome. Please check back as more material, old and new, will be added.

This website was created in April 2011 as an online archive for some of C.E. Chambers' published interviews, film critiques, and little-known Hawaiian historical information. It quickly evolved into a showcase for new material. Email address: info@vikingconfidential.com
